      "acrostic": "LOOK OUT FOR THESE UNGODLY MEN",
      "chapterPhrase": "His Letter stands Open, Outlining the threat of spiritual Kidnappers; recalling the Overthrow of the Underworld and wicked Townsmen, he exposes the Filthy dreamers who mock their Opponent and Reject truth, facing the Tragedy of Hypocrites and Errant stars; God's Spoken word Executes the Ungodly, so Notice the Guilty and their Overt sins, remaining Devout and Loyal, choosing to Yearn and show Mercies until the Exalted reveals His Nobility.",
